Package com.att.ads

This package contains authorization service, ads service, Data Manager and logging.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AdLog Customized Logger to enable and disable the logger as user required.
AdService Class to perform retrieve advertisement operation from server and assigned it in a provided view.
ATTAdView Use the ATTAdView class to embed advertisement content in your application.
ATTAdViewError Class encapsulates the error type, message and exception information.
AuthService Authorization operation performed and access tokens are stored in shared preferences.
Constants Class encapsulating all of the constants and some are default values.
DataManager DataManager is a Singleton class and manages the data loading requests.
 

Package com.att.ads Description

This package contains authorization service, ads service, Data Manager and logging.
